'''Aikhylu Chasma''' is a tectonic rift valley on [[Venus]], and the landing site of the ''[[Venera 9]]'' lander. It is located in [[Beta Regio]].<ref>[http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/109;jsessionid=0C671567E30A033483D9FFC558B1AFFD Aikhylu Chasma at the USGS Gazetteer of Planetary Nomenclature]</ref>

