== M == * [[Ferdinand Mannlicher]], along with Scottish Canadian [[James Paris Lee]], Mannlicher was particularly noted for inventing the [[Clip (ammunition)#En bloc|en-bloc clip]] charger-loading magazine system. * [[August Musger]], inventor of [[slow motion]].
