'''Rebecca Ann Jockusch''', Ph.D. ([[UC Berkeley]], 2001), is a Canadian chemist; she is an associate professor at the Department of Chemistry of the [[University of Toronto]] (UToronto) who is active in the field of [[mass spectrometry]].<ref>UToronto, 2018</ref>

